trans-unit.source: Women Adhesive Strapless Breast Lift Up Nipplecovers Sticky Invisible Backless Silicone Bra
trans-unit.target: Women Adhesive Strapless Breast Lift Up Nipplecovers Sticky Invisible Backless Silicone Bra

trans-unit.source:
MEDICAL GRADE MATERIAL: Self-adhesive, 100% safe & skin-friendly silicone, soft and comfortable to wear, suitable for sensitive skin. Strong sticky silicone conform to your figure seamlessly while staying in place, cover the entire breast nipple area elegantly. A delicate way to go bra-less.
NEW ENHANCED DESIGN: 2019 latest petal pasties come with an adhesive breast lift tape which make your breast instant lift and firm. The unique heart-shaped hollow design makes it lighter, thinner and more breathable than the previous generation. There are three size available, 3.35"diameter(suits for A/B Cup), 4"diameter(suits for C/D Cup) and 4.7" diameter(suits for DD/E Cup). Compared with the 2.8"diameter, the upgraded nipplecovers are large enough to provide better coverage for your breast.
A STAPLE IN ANY WOMAN’S WARDROBE: The skin color and thin-edged design make this bra invisible under your clothing in a comfortable and natural way. It is absolutely perfect for Tops, Shirts, Off Shoulder, Backless, Deep-V, Swimsuit, wedding dress, low cut outfits, low back dress like prom and homecoming dress or any formal evening dresses, it’s the best option for photo shoots and red carpet moments alike.
WASHABLE AND REUSABLE: Hand wash only, after each use, rinse with warm water below 30 ℃, and mild soap then air dry. After drying, the plastic sheets can be reattached on and put them in a bag for next use. Adopt premium silicone makes the nipple covers can be worn multi times without loss of stickiness.
WARM TIPS: DO NOT use moisturizers, perfumes, powders or other skin care products prior to use. Dry in the shade, not expose to the Sun. Exposure may reduce the stickiness of silicone; Sweat and high temperature may affect the stickiness of silica gel.
Ueiku Self Adhesive Strapless Breast Lift Reusable Silicone with Nipple Covers are great to protect and hide nipple. Keep your breast lifted, supported, and perky.

Size Ref:

♥ Medium: Diameter 3.35", suit for A/B Cup: 32A 32B 34A 36A 32C 34B 36B 38A
♥ Large: Diameter 4", suit for C/D Cup: 38B 34C 36C 32D 38C 34D 36D 38D
♥ X-Large: Diameter 4.7", suit for DD/E Cup: 38DD 40B 40C 40D 40DD

Wearing Steps:

♥ Step-1: Wipe the breasts with warm towel. Wipe all oil, dirt even sweat on body.
♥ Step-2: Put the nipple cover onto the nipple softly, making the outer edge of which be stuck to the skin.
♥ Step-3: With the upper body leaning forward, attach the chest to the chest and flatten the edges.
♥ Step-4: Wear clothing and complete.

Warm Tips:

♥ After each use, simply rinse the petals pasties with warm water below 30 ¡æ and mild soap, then air dry.
♥ Do not expose it to sun, air dry in the shade.
♥ If the breast is inflamed or damaged, it is best not to use the nipple covers temporarily.
♥ Unsuitable for breast-feeding women.
♥ Sweat and high temperature may affect the stickiness of silicone.
♥ The nippleless covers may not provide enough adhesion and support for larger breasts (F-cup or larger).
